reviews.text: Good place to hang out
The only mcdonald in chai wan. Always full of people
no problem at all. just another typical McDonald's.

Many oldies occupied seats and wait for tea time menus, not big for many tables, counter slow, pre order from app does not cover this shop, as any MacDonald, not too clean, but it is better than Causeway Bay and TST branches, has ice cream counter
They made it! It’s rather difficult to have a bun that is hard and stale. The coffee is not hot and the environment is not clean

reviews.text: A more recent car park than others in chai wan. But hourly rate is $21, not cheap.
It’s the nearest car park to Youth Square, where many performances are held.
Recently construction in progress, parking lot is lesser and hard to go up or down as it became single way at 1/F and 2/F.
我每天到經過興翠華邨商場，但近幾年有很多新移民入住，這個商場地方很大，但没有醫務所設備，私家醫生等。十分不方便，另外没有公眾電話设備。还有祗有一部框员机。不是豐銀行。這是我個人意見。

我在 Mccafe要了一個火腿三文治及鮮奶綠茶作早餐，餐後不停作嘔及頭暈。
在这裡享用早餐，早上有免费添饮服務。更可在店內看報或公用电腦。也可以手機或八達通支付收费购買食品。
由細食到大，唔理佢營養問題，只理佢味道已經可以比5星，扣果一分係無服務
